OL,3,CAlmost half of Welsh workers
OL,4,Cexperience sexual harassment, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FNearly half of employees in Wales have
OL,8,Fexperienced some form of sexual
OL,9,Fharassment in the workplace, according
OL,10,Fto a new survey.
OL,12,F46% of respondents to a Censuswide
OL,13,Fsurvey by TUC Cymru said they had been
OL,14,Fa victim of workplace sexual
OL,15,Fharassment, with 8% of employees
OL,16,Fsaying they didn't know how to report
OL,17,Fincidents when they occur.
