OL,3,CAlmost half of Welsh workers
OL,4,Cexperience sexual harassment, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FFrom October 2024, the Worker
OL,8,FProtection Act places further
OL,9,Fresponsibilities on employers to
OL,10,Fdiscipline or hold accountable those
OL,11,Fwho are found guilty of sexual
OL,12,Fharassment. The legislation includes
OL,13,Fharassment from customers, clients,
OL,14,Fservice users, or members of the
OL,15,Fpublic, and would include conduct in
OL,16,Fany event or situation related to work
OL,17,Fsuch as a Christmas party, client
OL,18,Fevent, or messaging between colleagues.
