OL,3,CAlmost half of Welsh workers
OL,4,Cexperience sexual harassment, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FKay Stevens, TSSA union rep, spoke
OL,8,Fabout her own experiences as both a
OL,9,Fvictim and an advocate: "I had a
OL,10,Fcolleague that just kept putting his
OL,11,Farms around me and touching me. I told
OL,12,Fhim that it made me feel very
OL,13,Funcomfortable, so he'd stop for a bit
OL,14,Fand then carry on doing it.
OL,16,F"I reported it to management, who told
OL,17,Fme he was just being friendly. I was
OL,18,Fso disappointed by their response `
OL,19,FI'd asked him to stop, so why hadn't
OL,20,Fhe?
