OL,3,CAlmost half of Welsh workers
OL,4,Cexperience sexual harassment, survey
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Now as a union rep, my experiences of
OL,8,Fworkplace sexual harassment have made
OL,9,Fme even more passionate about ensuring
OL,10,Fthat everyone is safe at work at all
OL,11,Ftimes. Everyone should feel safe in
OL,12,Fthe workplace, and they deserve to
OL,13,Fhave someone in their corner. Whether
OL,14,Fit's happening now or happened a long
OL,15,Ftime ago, I'd urge people to speak to
OL,16,Ftheir union reps ` we're here, we will
OL,17,Flisten, and we will act."
OL,19,FTUC Cymru has launched a campaign,
OL,20,Fcalled We'll Support You, to tackle
OL,21,Fsexual harassment in the workplace.
