OL,7,FShavanah Taj, TUC Cymru General
OL,8,FSecretary said: "Everyone deserves to
OL,9,Ffeel safe at work. It's shocking that,
OL,10,Fin 2025, nearly half of all workers in
OL,11,FWales have experienced sexual
OL,12,Fharassment at work. This has to stop.
OL,13,FAnd that's why we're launching our
OL,14,FWe'll Support You campaign.
